oads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-1218x1536.jpg 1218w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-1623x2048.jpg 1623w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-150x189.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1744px) 100vw, 1744px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201744%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-scaled.jpg 1744w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-728x918.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-768x969.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-1218x1536.jpg 1218w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-1623x2048.jpg 1623w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-150x189.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-13-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cauliflower gets toasted in the skillet first. Next, you add in the noodles with more butter and parmesan.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOn the side, toast some breadcrumbs.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIs there anything cozier than buttered noodles?! I think not. \u003cspan id=\"more-97933\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"toasted cauliflower buttered noodles\" width=\"1788\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/cauliflower-buttered-noodles/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Toasted Cauliflower Buttered Noodles.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-scaled.jpg 1788w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-728x896.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-768x945.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-1249x1536.jpg 1249w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-1665x2048.jpg 1665w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-150x185.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1788px) 100vw, 1788px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201788%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-scaled.jpg 1788w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-728x896.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-768x945.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-1249x1536.jpg 1249w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-1665x2048.jpg 1665w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-150x185.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-6-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA little bit of the starchy pasta water brings the whole thing together in a silky, creamy noodle way. These are so soft and savory and cheesy. They taste like heaven and have a tiny bit of crunch on top.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFresh herbs aren’t necessary, but add a little refreshing brightness. It’s a simple cozy dish that can make its way into your menu plan!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"toasted cauliflower buttered noodles\" width=\"1792\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/cauliflower-buttered-noodles/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Toasted Cauliflower Buttered Noodles.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-scaled.jpg 1792w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-728x894.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-768x943.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-1251x1536.jpg 1251w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-1668x2048.jpg 1668w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-150x184.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1792px) 100vw, 1792px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201792%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-scaled.jpg 1792w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-728x894.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-768x943.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-1251x1536.jpg 1251w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-1668x2048.jpg 1668w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-150x184.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eToasted Cauliflower Buttered Noodles\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-97948\" data-recipe-id=\"97948\" data-servings=\"2\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-8-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eToasted Cauliflower Buttered Noodles\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"97948\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e25\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e25\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe can\u0026#39;t get enough of these toasted cauliflower buttered noodles! Skillet toasted cauliflower florets are tossed with tender pasta noodles, lots of parmesan cheese, butter and toasty breadcrumbs. Major comfort food!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97948\" data-servings=\"2\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eshort cut pasta noodles\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(I use mafalda)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esmall to medium cauliflower,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecut into florets\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/land-o-lakes-unsalted-butter-1lb/-/A-13227053?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eunsalted butter\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003estarchy pasta water\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/signature-parmigiano-reggiano-cheese-7oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-85327169?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efreshly grated parmesan cheese\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eseasoned bread crumbs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003efresh herbs,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping (parsley, cilantro, basil, chives, etc)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97948\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97948-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring a pot of salted water to a boil and cook the pasta according to the instructions. Make sure to reserve ½ cup of the starchy pasta water. Make the cauliflower while the pasta cooks.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97948-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eCut the cauliflower into florets that are bite-sized. Heat 2 tablespoons of the butter in a large skillet over medium heat. Add the cauliflower with a pinch of salt and pepper and toss well. Cook, stirring often, until the cauliflower turns deeply golden broth, about 6 to 8 minutes. Stir in the garlic.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97948-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd the noodles to the skillet with the remaining butter. Toss well. Add the starchy pasta water. Add in the parmesan cheese and stir until it melts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97948-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat 1 more tablespoon of butter in a small skillet over medium heat. Add the breadcrumbs and stir to coat. Cook and stir for 5 minutes, until toasty. Sprinkle the breadcrumbs on top of the noodles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97948-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd some fresh herbs if you’d like, then serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"toasted cauliflower buttered noodles\" width=\"1654\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/cauliflower-buttered-noodles/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Toasted Cauliflower Buttered Noodles.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-scaled.jpg 1654w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-728x968.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-768x1022.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-1155x1536.jpg 1155w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-1540x2048.jpg 1540w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/toasted-cauliflower-buttered-noodles-12-150x200.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1654px) 100vw, 1654px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201654%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/